{"tid":1684000,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"燒山重批韓國瑜必定落選後 蔡英文與韓國瑜差距僅剩個位數","createTime":"2019-10-31T01:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T05:15:15.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca2f17d3528f8ac3b7fc9b32377bc80b3528c185","tid":1684000,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T01:42:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/J4bCv1h39MI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJ4bCv1h39MI&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA3aXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=f53eafb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/J4bCv1h39MI</a><br />\n26/10<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/article/1885421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F1885421&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA3aXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=ae09b10e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/article/1885421</a><br />\n2020總統大選倒數73天，根據《ETtoday新聞雲》今（30）日公布的最新民調顯示，在藍綠對決的情況下，總統蔡英文雖仍以42.1%的支持度領先國民黨總統參選人韓國瑜的33.1%，但兩人的差距已縮小至9個百分點；而若是在藍綠橘對戰的情況下，親民黨主席宋楚瑜支持度則只有7.9%。<br />\n民調顯示，在藍綠對決的情況下，蔡英文的支持度為42.1%，韓國瑜則為33.1%，相較於前次調查結果，蔡英文下降1.8個百分點，韓國瑜則微幅減少0.1個百分點，蔡英文領先幅度從10.7個百分點縮小為9百分點，與前次民調差距雖不大但已降至個位數。<br />\n另外，若宋楚瑜第5度親征總統大選，使2020大選變成「蔡韓宋」三腳督，蔡英文的支持度仍以39.7%排名居冠，其次為韓國瑜30.6%，最後為宋楚瑜7.9%。"},{"pid":"ffeee1c55768997b99c96706bde035475f75a6de","tid":1684000,"uid":256142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T01:47:25.000Z","msg":"其力量無人能擋<br />\n可惜誤入歧途<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3aa84b72fef9eb4bd59081d3da6a7376a47aad","tid":1684000,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T01:56:20.000Z","msg":"依條廢老D片 出一個block一個 on99"},{"pid":"fda0a15e6d4006ce06dedd27a908219aa97f0f99","tid":1684000,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T05:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/15/a2tmFj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F15%2Fa2tmFj.png&h=ea2bd8bb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}